---
title: Honey & Thyme Beef Tacos with Leafy Salad & Aioli
description: The secret to our colourful, Mediterranean-style beef tacos is all in the leafy goodness. Substituting Greek yoghurt for garlic aioli
lends a pleasant creaminess and finishing it with crumbly cheese means you can chomp down on these tasty delights without a
second thought.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-honey-thyme-beef-tacos-ae3a25b6.jpg
